<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.8">
<l>poṅkiya marilo rukāl poṉpeya rōṉaive ruva</l>
<l>aṅkava ṉākama ḷaintiṭ ṭāyiran tōḷeḻun tāṭa</l>
<l>paiṅkaṇi raṇṭeri kāṉṟa nīṇṭaye yiṟṟoṭu pēḻvāy</l>
<l>ciṅkavu ruvilva ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who appeared in the form of a lion, which emitted fire</l>
<l rend="indent">from two green eyes,</l>
<l>[With] a cavernous mouth with long fangs,</l>
<l rend="indent">rising [high] as his one-thousand arms moved,</l>
<l>Raging one time there in battle, slicing up the chest</l>
<l rend="indent">of the one named “Gold”</l>
<l>So that he was terrified, he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
